@startuml billing-entitlement-enforcement
title Billing Entitlement Enforcement and Plan Limits
hide footbox
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 16
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #111111
  LifeLineBorderColor #111111
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #111111
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorBorderColor #111111
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  GroupBorderColor #111111
  GroupBackgroundColor #EEEEEE
}

actor "Workspace User\nor Widget Visitor" as User
participant "App / Widget UI" as UI
participant "Routes +\nValidation" as Routes
participant "Auth + Workspace\nGuards" as Guards
participant "Domain Service\nInvite/File/Mailbox/SLA/Ticket" as Domain
participant "Billing\nEnforcement" as Enforcement
participant "Billing\nFoundation" as Foundation
participant "Billing Models\nSubscription/Entitlement/Usage" as BillingModels
participant "Domain Models\nMember/Invite/File/Mailbox/Ticket" as DomainModels

== 1. Protected product action ==
User -> UI: Create invite, upload file,\ncreate mailbox, configure SLA,\nor create ticket
UI -> Routes: Product endpoint request
Routes -> Guards: auth/workspace guards\nwhere endpoint is protected
Routes -> Domain: validated request

== 2. Load entitlement and usage ==
Domain -> Enforcement: assert allowed for action
Enforcement -> Foundation: ensureWorkspaceBillingFoundation()
Foundation -> BillingModels: load subscription, plan,\nentitlement, usage meter
Foundation -> DomainModels: count seats, invites,\nmailboxes, storage
Foundation -> BillingModels: recompute entitlement snapshot
Foundation --> Enforcement: limits, features, usage, flags

== 3. Check limit ==
Enforcement -> Enforcement: check partial block,\nseats/mailboxes/storage/uploads/SLA feature

== 4. Allow action or block ==
alt Allowed
  Enforcement --> Domain: allowed
  Domain -> DomainModels: create invite/file/mailbox/SLA\nor ticket
else Limit exceeded or feature unavailable
  Enforcement --> UI: standard error envelope\n409 billing limit/feature error
end

== 5. Update usage when implemented ==
Domain -> Foundation: increment uploads or tickets\nand refresh usage snapshot
Foundation -> BillingModels: update UsageMeter\nand Entitlement.usage
note over Domain,Foundation
Ticket creation records monthly usage but no hard ticket-create block is implemented.
Seat, mailbox, upload/storage, SLA feature, and partial-block checks are enforced.
end note

@enduml
